{"id":174,"ayahs":[{"number":179,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ ذَرَأْنَا لِجَهَنَّمَ كَثِيرًۭا مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ وَٱلْإِنسِ ۖ لَهُمْ قُلُوبٌۭ لَّا يَفْقَهُونَ بِهَا وَلَهُمْ أَعْيُنٌۭ لَّا يُبْصِرُونَ بِهَا وَلَهُمْ ءَاذَانٌۭ لَّا يَسْمَعُونَ بِهَآ ۚ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ كَٱلْأَنْعَٰمِ بَلْ هُمْ أَضَلُّ ۚ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْغَٰفِلُونَ","translation":"And most certainly have We destined for hell many of the invisible beings and men who have hearts with which they fail to grasp the truth, and eyes with which they fail to see, and ears with which they fail to hear. They are like cattle -nay, they are even less conscious of the right way: it is they, they who are the [truly] heedless!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1133.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":83737,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83738,"position":2,"arabic":"ذَرَأْنَا","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83739,"position":3,"arabic":"لِجَهَنَّمَ","translation":"জন্যে জাহান্নামের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83740,"position":4,"arabic":"كَثِيرًۭا","translation":"অনেককে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83741,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্যে হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83742,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","translation":"জিন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83743,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِنسِ ۖ","translation":"ও মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83745,"position":8,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"রয়েছে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83746,"position":9,"arabic":"قُلُوبٌۭ","translation":"অন্তরসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_179_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83747,"position":10,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"(কিন্তু) না","au